title: Low elo
body: why do low elo kids go ''look at the damage charts?'' like damage doesn't make you good kid. So annoying. Just had to rant about that. Swear they wouldn't know logic if it bit them in ass.

replies.body: well.. damage is a pretty good indicator
damage doesn't mean shit in low elo.
damage is an indicator if you are participating in team fights. objectives are important yes but so is team fights and getting picks.
